"Apartment" I wanted more, Such chauvinism, have to view again perhaps to appreciate. "Some Like it Hot" I viewed in Sweden 20 ? years ago. I'm sure it's alright if you get the beats of 60+yrs. ago references etc. I am a geek 4 such. Not to say I get it all, but upon re-viewing a movie can pick up on the social norms or inside gags... Love movies 1940-' 69 or later if not garbage formula that Hollywood sucks so .
